---
title: Korean Beef, Corn & Creamy Slaw Bowl with Fried Egg & Coriander
description: This sizzling hot Korean beef from the pan is a delight unparalleled. Delicious marinated beef and the joy of simplicity are winners in this dish. A sprinkle of crushed peanuts are the crowning glory of this brilliant twist on the weeknight dinner..

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
